==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grammatophyllum
<hw>Grammatophyllum</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small genus of large
epiphytic or terrestrial orchids of Southeastern Asia to Polynesia; the
giants of the <fam>Orchidaceae</fam> having long narrow leaves and
drooping flower clusters often 6 feet long.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Grammatophyllum</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

